01:15:31.600 --> 01:15:35.712
I'm just about an overflow.

01:15:35.712 --> 01:15:40.925
I hate poverty; you can't do nothing.

01:15:43.457 --> 01:15:45.540
You go, "Well, what are you going to do?

01:15:45.540 --> 01:15:50.187
Oh, you got to work harder and have five jobs.

01:15:57.040 --> 01:15:57.475
" No.

01:15:57.475 --> 01:16:03.120
If the world can have it, how come we can't?

01:16:03.120 --> 01:16:04.747
We're His children.

01:16:04.747 --> 01:16:17.417
If Warren Buffett can have it, if Bill Gates, who's making all the pharmakeia stuff trying to give people stuff in their arms—how much more can we as children of God?

01:16:17.417 --> 01:16:19.230
Why not?

01:16:19.680 --> 01:16:35.685
I just stretch out and believe God that by the end of 2025, the next nine weeks, you're going to be completely debt-free.

01:16:51.543 --> 01:16:51.977
I just feel like I say that inside my spirit to stir up to believe God for big.

01:16:51.977 --> 01:16:54.000
Close this year out.

01:16:54.000 --> 01:16:54.480
Yes.

01:16:54.480 --> 01:16:55.369
Believe in bigger.

01:16:55.369 --> 01:16:59.160
Now, that might tick some of you off, but whatever.

01:16:59.160 --> 01:17:00.760
That's what I'm believing.

01:17:00.760 --> 01:17:03.963
Why not believe bigger?

01:17:03.963 --> 01:17:12.329
To be completely healed from the top of your head to the sole of your feet.

01:17:12.329 --> 01:17:14.475
Now, nothing missing, nothing broken.

01:17:14.475 --> 01:17:20.440
No more diabetics, no more cancer, no more heart disease.

01:17:20.440 --> 01:17:21.320
Believing God.

01:17:24.973 --> 01:17:43.977
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you're the God of restoration of my flesh, that I'm healed and whole and well of heart problems or brain problems or whatever you may be overcoming in your household.

01:17:46.440 --> 01:17:49.600
You may be wheelchair-bound, you may be bedridden—come out of that.

01:17:49.600 --> 01:17:59.469
There's an expiration date for what you're believing God for.

01:17:59.469 --> 01:18:06.950
I've seen God do it time and time again, and I believe He'll do it again.

01:18:06.950 --> 01:18:09.980
Glory to God.

01:18:26.650 --> 01:18:27.280
Thank you, Lord.

01:18:30.430 --> 01:18:30.760
You okay?

01:18:30.760 --> 01:18:31.280
Yeah.

01:18:31.280 --> 01:18:32.840
Your nose is running.

01:18:32.840 --> 01:18:35.480
I don't know, it keeps trying to sneeze.

01:18:35.480 --> 01:18:36.560
I'm sorry.

01:18:36.560 --> 01:18:39.223
The devil's such an idiot.

01:18:41.178 --> 01:18:45.766
It seems like when I came on, my eyes started watering.

01:18:45.766 --> 01:18:47.297
I know, love.

01:18:47.297 --> 01:18:49.093
It's the glory; you're crying.

01:18:49.093 --> 01:18:52.900
I see it's Jesus moving on you.

01:18:52.900 --> 01:18:53.785
Sorry, y'all.

01:18:53.785 --> 01:18:54.836
I love you.

01:18:54.836 --> 01:18:55.844
It's the glory.

01:18:55.844 --> 01:19:03.095
She isn't crying; those aren't tears from allergies or anything.

01:19:03.095 --> 01:19:06.305
That's tears from Jesus.

01:19:06.305 --> 01:19:08.040
I love you.

01:19:16.231 --> 01:19:16.453
Praise God.

01:19:16.453 --> 01:19:16.898
Hallelujah.

01:19:16.898 --> 01:19:24.067
Well, I don't know if that made you happy, but it made me happy.

01:19:24.067 --> 01:19:35.244
I still stir it up just to inspire myself to be a contender.

01:19:35.244 --> 01:19:39.320
I could have been a contender.

01:19:39.320 --> 01:19:40.800
I'm a contender.

01:19:40.800 --> 01:19:46.880
I'm believing God.

01:19:46.880 --> 01:19:49.307
Stretch your faith.

01:19:49.307 --> 01:19:52.610
Get some spiritual stretch marks.

01:19:52.610 --> 01:19:58.180
Like a pregnant woman gets stretch marks, get pregnant with what God has for you.

01:19:58.180 --> 01:19:59.700
Stretch your faith.

01:19:59.700 --> 01:20:11.225
Why not get pregnant with something big from God?

01:20:11.225 --> 01:20:15.204
Not like a baby, baby; I'm talking about vision.

01:20:15.204 --> 01:20:19.417
Get pregnant with a vision.

01:20:19.417 --> 01:20:21.110
Stretch yourself.

01:20:36.191 --> 01:20:36.422
Have some stretch marks.

01:20:36.422 --> 01:20:37.347
It shows growth.

01:20:37.347 --> 01:20:38.929
That's a sign of growth.

01:20:38.929 --> 01:20:41.340
Stretch marks are a sign of growth.

01:20:41.340 --> 01:20:44.470
It shows growth.

01:20:44.480 --> 01:20:47.963
Stretch yourself, you know, believe God for big.

01:20:54.440 --> 01:20:54.600
I just am trying to stretch.

01:20:54.600 --> 01:21:01.811
I want big spiritual stretch marks, because I'm believing God for big.

01:21:09.980 --> 01:21:10.170
I'm pregnant with something spiritual, supernatural, big.

01:21:10.170 --> 01:21:10.550
Yes.

01:21:10.550 --> 01:21:15.160
I'm not a female, but I'm believing God.

01:21:20.264 --> 01:21:20.452
You know what I'm saying?

01:21:20.880 --> 01:21:22.895
You got to get pregnant with something.

01:21:22.895 --> 01:21:23.900
Believe God.

01:21:23.900 --> 01:21:25.240
Stop thinking small.

01:21:25.240 --> 01:21:35.800
Come out of that "woe is me" poverty mentality of thinking, "Well, we're going to always be that way, Bob.

01:21:35.800 --> 01:21:40.120
" I'm not going to believe that way, Diana.

01:21:40.120 --> 01:21:43.937
We're going to get out of this.

01:21:43.937 --> 01:21:46.750
Give God something to work with.

01:21:46.750 --> 01:21:49.360
I'm pregnant with a vision and ministry.

01:21:49.360 --> 01:22:02.496
I'm pregnant with the Holy Ghost and what He's got for me and my family, and I've got stretch marks because I'm believing and I'm huge in it.

01:22:02.496 --> 01:22:07.709
You can say, "How many months are you?

01:22:16.367 --> 01:22:16.773
" I'm past nine months.

01:22:16.773 --> 01:22:19.600
It's time to deliver this spiritual baby.

01:22:31.370 --> 01:22:31.785
We're believing God for big for ministry on another level.

01:22:42.536 --> 01:22:42.800
I am anointed to do ministry in a way the world is not familiar with, all for the glory of God.

01:22:42.800 --> 01:22:56.933
Like Pastor Chip says, I believe I'm anointed to do YouTube in a way that the world is not familiar with, all for the glory of God.

01:22:56.933 --> 01:23:03.823
We're pregnant with a vision that we're going to have this spiritual baby before the end of 2025.

01:23:03.823 --> 01:23:12.450
It's time to thrive in the rest of 2025, not just barely get by.

01:23:12.450 --> 01:23:21.907
It's time to thrive in the name of Jesus and believe God for overflow.

01:23:21.907 --> 01:23:25.103
Why not me?

01:23:25.103 --> 01:23:25.880
Why not you?

01:23:25.880 --> 01:23:30.820
Give God something to work with.

01:23:30.820 --> 01:23:45.671
I'm pregnant with a vision and Oral Roberts says at his campus, we see it all the time: "Make no little plans here.

01:23:45.671 --> 01:23:46.596
" Don't think small.

01:23:50.173 --> 01:23:50.480
You think too small.

01:23:50.480 --> 01:23:55.330
That's what he said even this last time.

01:23:55.330 --> 01:23:56.920
"You're thinking too small, Brandon.

01:23:56.920 --> 01:23:57.580
Too small.

01:23:59.977 --> 01:24:00.314
You got to stretch.

01:24:13.547 --> 01:24:13.733
" We were driving around even yesterday.

01:24:15.493 --> 01:24:15.662
Didn't he say that you're thinking too small?

01:24:15.662 --> 01:24:16.462
Be a contender.

01:24:16.462 --> 01:24:16.924
Stretch.

01:24:16.924 --> 01:24:19.118
Believe God for bigger.

01:24:19.118 --> 01:24:21.193
Hallelujah.

01:24:21.193 --> 01:24:23.360
Praise God.

01:24:23.360 --> 01:24:24.480
Thank you, Lord.

01:24:24.480 --> 01:24:25.420
We're so grateful.

01:24:25.420 --> 01:24:26.973
Did it inspire you tonight?

01:24:26.973 --> 01:24:28.560
Did it fan that flame?

01:24:28.560 --> 01:24:32.671
Did it give you some hope, some wind in your sails?

01:24:32.876 --> 01:24:48.560
I always want to come on and give you some hope from the Holy Spirit, to give you wind in your sails that your circumstance can change, that you're not stuck.

01:25:10.273 --> 01:25:10.951
A rut is just something you keep walking around in, right?

01:25:21.360 --> 01:25:21.680
You got in a rut.

01:25:26.011 --> 01:25:26.206
You keep walking the same path.

01:25:26.206 --> 01:25:29.947
I don't want to be in a rut.

01:25:30.333 --> 01:25:33.895
I'm not stuck.

01:25:37.258 --> 01:25:37.969
I'm going to get out.

01:25:37.969 --> 01:25:41.280
Don't get in this spiritual rut.

01:25:41.280 --> 01:25:43.771
A spiritual rut is no good.

01:25:58.320 --> 01:25:58.580
I want out and I want to get out of that mentality.

01:25:58.580 --> 01:26:00.960
Say, "God, I want more of you.

01:26:00.960 --> 01:26:01.800
Show me.

01:26:01.800 --> 01:26:07.085
I want to have more of a revelation of who You are in me.

01:26:07.085 --> 01:26:13.640
Christ in me, the hope of glory.

01:26:13.640 --> 01:26:20.067
" Thank you, Lord, for our health and all that You provided for us.

01:26:20.067 --> 01:26:25.080
Father, we're so grateful and thankful for everything You've done for us.

01:26:25.080 --> 01:26:27.850
We don't take any of it for granted.

01:26:27.850 --> 01:26:32.427
No matter the small or the big, God provides it all.

01:26:32.427 --> 01:26:46.527
It may be like I was with one person one time and the lady gave the person a free cup of coffee.

01:26:48.760 --> 01:26:54.075
I said, "Glory to God, a free cup of coffee today.

01:26:54.075 --> 01:26:58.765
" And they said, "Oh, I don't sweat the small stuff.

01:26:58.765 --> 01:27:06.680
" But you've got to give God praise even for the small cup of coffee.

01:27:06.680 --> 01:27:08.811
Just the generosity of somebody.

01:27:17.115 --> 01:27:18.573
The free cup of coffee, the free biscuit, a free donut.

01:27:18.573 --> 01:27:23.560
Somebody saying, "Hey, I'd like to give you this stick of gum.

01:27:31.067 --> 01:27:33.245
" But it's something you didn't have to work for.

01:27:33.245 --> 01:27:35.560
It's sweatless victory.

01:27:35.560 --> 01:27:41.775
Being thankful for everything, in all that you do, in word and deed, do all for the glory of God.

01:27:44.240 --> 01:27:46.610
I give God praise for the small and the large, but even for the microscopic.

01:27:46.610 --> 01:27:48.660
Thank you, Father.

01:27:48.660 --> 01:27:53.285
He's looking for a heart of praise and thanksgiving.

01:27:53.285 --> 01:28:02.760
As we get ready to go into the Thanksgiving season in America, are you thankful for what you do have?

01:28:02.760 --> 01:28:06.191
Or are you a spoiled Braden?

01:28:06.191 --> 01:28:08.369
"Oh, that's not enough, Dad.

01:28:08.369 --> 01:28:09.240
" No, no.

01:28:14.320 --> 01:28:15.720
Thank you.

01:28:15.720 --> 01:28:20.325
Being faithful to give Him praise in the little things, right?

01:28:20.325 --> 01:28:27.600
Because when the big things come along, you don't take for granted even the smallest thing.

01:28:27.600 --> 01:28:33.707
Well, or any kind of change that you've seen in your life.

01:28:36.920 --> 01:28:45.160
You may have just a little bit of change, but give God praise for that one little thing.

01:28:45.160 --> 01:28:49.760
Well, I was not able to move.

01:28:49.760 --> 01:28:57.149
I can't move my leg, but I can move my toe.

01:28:58.320 --> 01:28:59.907
Oh, God, you're so good for my little toe.

01:29:00.360 --> 01:29:03.230
God, you're so faithful for my little toe.

01:29:03.230 --> 01:29:12.870
Thank you, Lord, for my toe was able to be moved.

01:29:12.880 --> 01:29:18.823
And I'm telling you, you give God praise for that little toe.

01:29:18.823 --> 01:29:22.420
And look at what he does.

01:29:22.420 --> 01:29:29.080
That's whenever Noah sent out the bird like Billy always teaches.

01:29:29.405 --> 01:29:36.275
He said he sent out the bird and it brought back an olive leaf.

01:29:36.275 --> 01:29:39.240
Just a small little bird, little bitty dove.

01:29:39.240 --> 01:29:49.571
Go out there and get that little bitty thing that fit in that little—but it was a sign of hope to know that the flood was receding.

01:29:54.827 --> 01:29:55.920
It was at that point that Noah knew that the flood was over.

01:30:00.520 --> 01:30:03.124
It was just such a small little sign, but it was in that sign that everything started to change.

01:30:04.698 --> 01:30:06.640
And he could give God praise for the olive leaf.

01:30:06.640 --> 01:30:11.898
Just a little bitty olive leaf in that dove's beak, but it was a sign that the flood was over.

01:30:19.880 --> 01:30:21.731
You may have just an olive leaf in your life today, but that's a sign that your flood is over.

01:30:26.738 --> 01:30:28.409
You need to start giving God praise for the olive leaf.

01:30:32.770 --> 01:30:47.951
You may just have that olive leaf in your life and you don't see anything else, but the flood waters are all around you; but God gave you your first sign that the flood is over.

01:30:47.951 --> 01:30:53.498
It's time to give God praise for the olive leaf.

01:30:53.498 --> 01:30:58.880
I give him praise for my Megan all the time.

01:30:58.880 --> 01:31:00.910
We see even more today.

01:31:00.910 --> 01:31:04.404
It's fun the way she is.

01:31:04.404 --> 01:31:12.716
Her personality is coming more alive all the time.

01:31:14.304 --> 01:31:18.240
And we talked about it.

01:31:29.450 --> 01:31:29.660
I said, 'You can see my Megan.

01:31:29.660 --> 01:31:33.909
We have more than an olive leaf.

01:31:33.909 --> 01:31:39.911
I feel like I have an olive branch some days' from where we used to be.

01:31:39.911 --> 01:31:43.267
We're not where we want to be.

01:31:43.267 --> 01:31:47.217
But you don't get what you don't get, you know.

01:31:47.217 --> 01:31:48.680
I remember when.

01:31:48.680 --> 01:31:50.280
Thank you for the olive leaf.

01:31:50.280 --> 01:31:52.830
Thank you for the branch.

01:31:52.830 --> 01:31:56.020
Thank you, Father, for the double olive leaf.

01:31:56.020 --> 01:31:58.034
Thank you, Father, for where we are.

01:31:58.034 --> 01:32:00.880
We're not where we used to be.

01:32:09.080 --> 01:32:09.280
That's why I'm trying to tell you, go into these next couple of days with thanksgiving.

01:32:09.280 --> 01:32:17.090
Father, I may not have all my house paid off, but I don't know how much you may owe.

01:32:17.090 --> 01:32:24.875
You say you have a $100,000 house, and you may have $50,000 of it paid for.

01:32:24.875 --> 01:32:34.320
Thank you, Lord, that I may have half of it paid for.

01:32:34.320 --> 01:32:39.977
Watch what God does with a grateful heart.

01:32:39.977 --> 01:32:43.160
Even consider with a half.

01:32:43.160 --> 01:32:52.195
And don't forget the little leaves because all of those leaves add up to a full branch.

01:33:02.286 --> 01:33:03.092
Thank you, Lord, that I have half of my student loan.

01:33:03.092 --> 01:33:08.782
Thank you, Lord, that my doctor bills are paid off.

01:33:08.782 --> 01:33:12.784
Thank you, Lord, I may only have $10,000 paid, but boy, it's the first 10,000.

01:33:12.784 --> 01:33:16.563
I got my olive leaf.

01:33:35.533 --> 01:33:35.787
I may not be able to move all my foot, Lord, but I can move my toe.

01:33:35.787 --> 01:33:37.309
I can wiggle my nose.

01:33:39.291 --> 01:33:49.213
I may not be able to move all my—they may be paralyzed all the way, but I can wiggle my nose a little bit, something.

01:33:50.160 --> 01:33:56.497
I might be able to blink my eye, but I'm doing it by faith.

01:34:08.060 --> 01:34:08.320
I may have an olive leaf, Lord, but I got to move this.

01:34:09.880 --> 01:34:10.150
And I'm so grateful.

01:34:10.150 --> 01:34:13.240
Thank you, Jesus.

01:34:13.240 --> 01:34:18.360
Thank you, Father, for all that you've done.

01:34:18.360 --> 01:34:21.820
Glory to your name, Lord.

01:34:21.820 --> 01:34:24.400
We're so grateful, Father.

01:34:24.400 --> 01:34:28.422
Thank you for the tank of gas to get to church today.

01:34:28.422 --> 01:34:30.416
Thank you for the Taco Bell.

01:34:30.416 --> 01:34:41.453
It may not be the best taco I had today, but God, I had something in my stomach.

01:34:41.453 --> 01:34:43.326
Thank you for that taco, Lord.

01:34:43.326 --> 01:34:47.103
Thank you for that stale bread.

01:35:01.653 --> 01:35:01.898
It may have had mold on it, but I had something in my stomach today and I could pick off the mold, Lord.

01:35:13.440 --> 01:35:13.640
And I'm so grateful that you provided even a stale piece of bread with mold on it.

01:35:26.257 --> 01:35:26.520
Lord, you're so good to me.

01:35:26.520 --> 01:35:31.840
Watch what God's got to do with that.

01:35:31.840 --> 01:35:34.120
I've been there.

01:35:34.120 --> 01:35:39.640
And it isn't always easy for your flesh.

01:35:39.640 --> 01:35:44.590
Your flesh will be screaming, 'What are you doing, crazy?

01:35:45.578 --> 01:35:46.591
Are you kidding me?

01:35:46.591 --> 01:35:50.580
You're praising for a piece of molded bread?

01:35:50.580 --> 01:35:54.360
' But God's so good to Brandon.

01:35:54.360 --> 01:35:56.230
God's been good to Diana.

01:35:56.230 --> 01:35:58.783
God's been good to me.

01:35:58.783 --> 01:36:13.580
Remember that time when we were in the parking lot and we didn't have the money to buy our kids shoes and you found a $20 bill blowing in the wind and you started crying.

01:36:13.580 --> 01:36:16.700
You ran back to me and we were believing God.

01:36:21.080 --> 01:36:21.314
We didn't have nothing.

01:36:23.467 --> 01:36:23.853
And you found $20.

01:36:28.200 --> 01:36:28.427
And you said, 'Brandon, I found $20 today.

01:36:28.427 --> 01:36:29.333
I found $20.

01:36:30.760 --> 01:36:33.160
I can buy our baby some shoes.

01:36:33.160 --> 01:36:39.496
' And so you went into Walmart and you got the shoes and we were able to put the shoes on, but we didn't have it.

01:36:39.496 --> 01:36:44.780
But it was the moment that we gave God praise for the 20 that God made a way.

01:36:45.000 --> 01:36:47.451
I don't know who lost the 20.

01:36:47.451 --> 01:36:56.716
I'm sorry that they lost it, but it was a blessing to me that it was blowing in the wind.

01:36:56.716 --> 01:36:59.827
Yeah, it came from—maybe it was an angel.

01:37:05.800 --> 01:37:06.100
I don't know.

01:37:06.100 --> 01:37:08.213
I'm just saying it was God.

01:37:09.440 --> 01:37:12.160
And I'll never forget that $20 bill.

01:37:12.160 --> 01:37:15.160
We still talk about it today.

01:37:25.520 --> 01:37:25.960
It was God that provided the $20.

01:37:35.840 --> 01:37:36.058
And we had a Holy Ghost dance, didn't we, over that?

01:37:36.058 --> 01:37:40.680
We rejoiced over the $20 to give him praise for the baby's shoes.

01:37:40.680 --> 01:37:42.888
'Well, that seems so small, Brandon.

01:37:42.888 --> 01:37:44.872
' It was huge to us.

01:37:44.872 --> 01:37:48.005
When you don't have $20, $20 is a lot.

01:37:49.735 --> 01:37:50.245
It doesn't matter what it was.

01:37:50.245 --> 01:37:54.307
I mean, it could have been 10,000 at that time.

01:37:54.307 --> 01:37:56.880
20 bucks was 20 bucks in our household.

01:37:56.880 --> 01:38:06.770
We were excited about $20 when you don't have nothing and you're digging out pennies out of the couch cushions trying to find whatever you can find or going through ditches and looking for Coke cans.

01:38:06.770 --> 01:38:08.480
I'm serious.

01:38:08.480 --> 01:38:10.080
Isn't God faithful?

01:38:15.107 --> 01:38:15.369
So, I'm just trying to inspire you to be thankful going into believing God for your needs.

01:38:15.369 --> 01:38:25.971
That's the seed of praise, seed of thanksgiving, seed of being grateful going into believing for your manifestation all the way through the rest of 2025.

01:38:30.436 --> 01:38:30.551
I never go at him like that, saying, 'I earned this.

01:38:42.623 --> 01:38:43.051
I tithe.

01:38:45.667 --> 01:38:45.853
I give.

01:38:45.853 --> 01:38:47.344
' He doesn't owe me nothing.

01:38:47.344 --> 01:38:51.960
My mentality is the tithe was his in the first place.

01:38:57.810 --> 01:38:58.165
I didn't do anything.

01:39:09.960 --> 01:39:10.500
I gave him what was already his, his 10 percent.

01:39:17.160 --> 01:39:17.535
And I just wanted to be a blessing to him.

01:39:17.535 --> 01:39:25.520
But I look at it and say, 'Lord, I did what I could to help your gospel get out.

01:39:25.520 --> 01:39:32.120
' But my attitude is any overflow is his mercy.

